{"tid":1405980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地8月5日唔好一朝早搞馬路d坑渠蓋","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T01:54:12.000Z","uid":150625,"like":528,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"3c5994841fb535a8e31cbf1ffc8799c24a567d3f","tid":1405980,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-dQOTJMs4H7E/U4FSJXS5wHI/AAAAAAABE3g/5qwKfWcP7So/s1600/Inspection+Cover_PCCW.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-dQOTJMs4H7E%2FU4FSJXS5wHI%2FAAAAAAABE3g%2F5qwKfWcP7So%2Fs1600%2FInspection%2BCover_PCCW.JPG&h=ba9b6a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: large;\">作為一隻住大西北港豬我好鐘意去中環返工架<br />\n但如果大家邊日深夜或者一朝早搵大型十字鐵筆抽起左重要大馬路既坑渠蓋</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/18/52/10185238_986957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F18%2F52%2F10185238_986957.jpg&h=0395090f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲要將個蓋唔知收左去邊冇得好快蓋返<br />\n條路好危險完全唔可以行車架</span><br />\n<br />\n渠蓋失蹤現大窿公路索命 積架中招 全車報銷 渠署靠害<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180220/00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180220%2F00174_001.html&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=933d49a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180220/00174_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n爛渠蓋劏爆胎六車輪陷<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140425/00407_047.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140425%2F00407_047.html&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=8ef9c339\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140425/00407_047.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">個蓋唔見既話仲要唔知幾多日先搞掂<br />\nd路因為安全問題封晒我點返工呀 尤其地鐵又同時比你地塞住既話</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: large;\">求下你地唔好呀</span>"},{"pid":"a2c03312f585f6ac3de6508ba38fb1e551713d31","tid":1405980,"uid":150625,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好10連"},{"pid":"d5f523efbcc6b852c7ed82fd63fb4089cdaa9b9d","tid":1405980,"uid":150625,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好10連"},{"pid":"0486e560d3a2dd9c3bcd29e0ba0dc0d49be31720","tid":1405980,"uid":7912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06c8bd84a5a91fefa4ce19f8139da591f6c44993","tid":1405980,"uid":150625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好10連"},{"pid":"ce8e47e091c94ddf0ca67a49daee21f8532d6926","tid":1405980,"uid":190141,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:32.000Z","msg":"真係好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6f5f1444168a4fbe5bb7a1ec94f64eb4d25bec","tid":1405980,"uid":150625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好10連"},{"pid":"4af44daba70ba2da24bccd9079a71355420cf093","tid":1405980,"uid":8762,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"大家要小心安全呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85f0934c0d86c8741b57cc6174301379f94790f","tid":1405980,"uid":193378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:47.000Z","msg":"支持 但係搵工具需時"},{"pid":