a><br />\n<br />\n爛渠蓋劏爆胎六車輪陷<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140425/00407_047.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140425%2F00407_047.html&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=8ef9c339\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140425/00407_047.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">個蓋唔見既話仲要唔知幾多日先搞掂<br />\nd路因為安全問題封晒我點返工呀 尤其地鐵又同時比你地塞住既話</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: large;\">求下你地唔好呀</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />判頭大把蓋擺係倉啦"},{"pid":"731fc12dea1a790ffeade0a888097d301a9edd86","tid":1405980,"uid":200135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:42:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e0ef89405ff6b5680ec82a4d64f7ee9f9646056","tid":1405980,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:44:32.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"a4378b4c33a695d1dd054dd724967c824c54a356","tid":1405980,"uid":295089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"求下你地聽日千祈唔好封青馬橋"},{"pid":"a99412e27db0a93c6a66ccef09e2781a8d50727a","tid":1405980,"uid":47136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:46:24.000Z","msg":"咁做好危險,仲返唔返工好?"},{"pid":"b8f8bb8095c550a518efb2efdafea6cd3bdeb357","tid":1405980,"uid":201889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"跌落沙井 (渠蓋下面叫沙井), <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">死過好多人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n很多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">消防員</